{"tid":1551450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"破壞交通燈同升降機問題","createTime":"2019-09-08T04:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T05:02:52.000Z","uid":55597,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"78ed83ddf05b72be650c0fc18ac7c6af0098e1cd","tid":1551450,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:16:04.000Z","msg":"地區工作人員搵我傳達訊息<br />\n<br />\n破壞交通燈除了影響交通，還會對道路使用者產生影響，例如長者、行動不便及視障人士<br />\n而破壞升降機會令輪椅人士不能前往某些地方或無法使用某些服務<br />\n嚴重可能影響生命安全<br />\n佢地真係唔可以話坐的士就得<br />\n<br />\n對於政府同港鐵嘅不負責任態度，大家都好憤怒，完全理解<br />\n但係影響目標運作同服務使用者之間搵下平衡<br />\n當中可能有長者、 行動不便人士同視障人士都想參與運動<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位集思廣益"},{"pid":"18dea564f3703e27dcba9598ff62a669cb6bf1b1","tid":1551450,"uid":261082,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:19:18.000Z","msg":"今朝881個主持may 姐話燒紙皮搞到捨紙皮婆婆冇得捨好慘，真係無奈"},{"pid":"b01eec67aba4ae24ee79efbee15e1b10430468fd","tid":1551450,"uid":48011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"18dea564f3703e27dcba9598ff62a669cb6bf1b1","tid":1551450,"uid":261082,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:19:18.000Z","msg":"今朝881個主持may 姐話燒紙皮搞到捨紙皮婆婆冇得捨好慘，真係無奈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:23:39.000Z","msg":"佢係咪唔知依家廢紙有幾唔值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8081e6a1713e425ccc17c85bdfe4686bdd0b0147","tid":1551450,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18dea564f3703e27dcba9598ff62a669cb6bf1b1","tid":1551450,"uid":261082,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:19:18.000Z","msg":"今朝881個主持may 姐話燒紙皮搞到捨紙皮婆婆冇得捨好慘，真係無奈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:27:47.000Z","msg":"一噸紙皮都唔知有冇100蚊"},{"pid":"c6ffeb88eaed0021a7d506869903ad62c0a0c704","tid":1551450,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:28:20.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span